    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Inland waterway vessels used to push groups of barges; for general assistance vessels employed at sea or in and around harbors, use "tugboats."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
